message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with sound and music computing. cs.LG is also likely as it deals with machine learning techniques. cs.CV is another possibility as it deals with computer vision and image processing, which can be applied to spectrograms. cs.AI and cs.CL are less likely but still possible as they deal with artificial intelligence and natural language processing, respectively, which can also be applied to audio data.
